## UI / Design Patterns

### Icons
Remix Icon 4.6.0 via CDN: `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.6.0/fonts/remixicon.css`  
Loaded in `layout.tsx` (afterInteractive script injector + noscript). Class pattern: `ri-*-line`.

### Images
- `next/image` with per-app Supabase `remotePatterns`
- Platform rule: unique AI-generated images per page; upload to `site-assets/images/`; public URL: `https://<ref>.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/site-assets/images/<filename>`
- Naming: `<route-prefix>_<section><index>.jpg` (e.g. `cb_coding-guide_hero01.jpg`)

### CSS
Tailwind v4 — `@import "tailwindcss"` in `globals.css`; `@tailwindcss/postcss` in `postcss.config.mjs`

### Fonts (per app)
- `client-template`: Inter (`--font-inter`)
- `cipher-billing`: Marcellus (`--font-marcellus`) + Montserrat (`--font-montserrat`)
- `sweet-media`: Outfit / Cormorant (CSS variables)

### Elementor Migration (cipher-billing only)
- Vendor CSS in `src/styles/vendor-elementor-reimbursement/` (frontend.min.css, post-8.css, post-271.css, post-571.css, widget-*.min.css)
- Route bundles: `src/styles/elementor-reimbursement-bundle.css`, `elementor-coding-guide-bundle.css`, `elementor-kit-fallback.css`
- Route layouts import the bundle CSS → Turbopack bundles into route chunk (head-loaded)
- HTML source: `src/views/*/migrated-raw.html`
- Loader: `loadCipherElementorFullPage` (full HTML) or `loadCipherElementorBody` (sliced at first content section)
- Full-page wrapper: `<div className="elementor-kit-8 w-full overflow-x-hidden">` — do NOT add `cipher-migrated-html` class on Elementor routes

